msgid "Jay CRM Assistant"
msgstr "Jay - Assistant CRM"

msgid "Jay Connection"
msgstr "Connexion Jay"

msgid "Connect your Odoo instance to Jay AI CRM Assistant. Jay lets you manage your CRM with voice commands."
msgstr "Connectez votre instance Odoo a Jay, assistant CRM par intelligence artificielle. Jay vous permet de gerer votre CRM par commandes vocales."

msgid "Jay Instance URL"
msgstr "URL de l'instance Jay"

msgid "Jay Account Email"
msgstr "Email du compte Jay"

msgid "Jay API Key"
msgstr "Cle API Jay"

msgid "Connected"
msgstr "Connecte"

msgid "Test Connection"
msgstr "Tester la connexion"

msgid "Disconnect"
msgstr "Deconnecter"

msgid "How it works"
msgstr "Comment ca marche"

msgid "Voice-to-CRM"
msgstr "Voix vers CRM"

msgid "Record a voice note in Jay, and your contacts, deals, activities, and meetings are automatically synced to Odoo."
msgstr "Enregistrez une note vocale dans Jay, et vos contacts, opportunites, activites et rendez-vous sont automatiquement synchronises dans Odoo."

msgid "Supported objects"
msgstr "Objets supportes"

msgid "Contacts, Companies, Opportunities (CRM Leads), Activities, Calendar Events, and Notes."
msgstr "Contacts, Societes, Opportunites (Pistes CRM), Activites, Evenements du calendrier et Notes."

msgid "Anti-duplicate"
msgstr "Anti-doublons"

msgid "Jay detects existing records before creating new ones to keep your data clean."
msgstr "Jay detecte les enregistrements existants avant d'en creer de nouveaux pour garder vos donnees propres."

msgid "Please fill in both the Jay Instance URL and API Key before testing."
msgstr "Veuillez remplir l'URL de l'instance Jay et la cle API avant de tester."

msgid "Connection successful"
msgstr "Connexion reussie"

msgid "Jay is connected and ready to sync your CRM data."
msgstr "Jay est connecte et pret a synchroniser vos donnees CRM."

msgid "Disconnected"
msgstr "Deconnecte"

msgid "Jay has been disconnected from Odoo."
msgstr "Jay a ete deconnecte d'Odoo."
